      ],
      "question": "How often is the data refreshed?",
      "answer": "Public visitors refresh every 2 hours (aligned to local clock boundaries such as 12:00am, 2:00am, and 4:00am). Signed-in free accounts refresh every 15 minutes (:00, :15, :30, :45). Premium checks for updates every 15 seconds and refreshes when source data changes.",
